overview: Filmed at the O2 Arena in Dublin on 27 November 2009, this was the last gig of Kasabian's 2009 arena tour. It was released on DVD in 2011, as part of the deluxe edition of their 'Velociraptor!' album.  The setlist was: 1. Julie & The Moth Man  2. Underdog  3. Where Did All The Love Go?  4. Swarfiga  5. Shoot The Runner  6. Cutt Off  7. Processed Beats  8. West Ryder Silver Bullet  9. Thick As Thieves  10. Take Aim  11. Empire  12. Last Trip (In Flight)  13. I.D.  14. Ladies And Gentlemen (Roll The Dice)  15. Fire  16. Fast Fuse  17. The Doberman  18. Club Foot  19. Vlad The Impaler  20. Stuntman  21. L.S.F. (Lost Souls Forever)
title: Kasabian: Live from Dublin
